These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: water, tea
House: gothic-revival, colonial
1. House:gothic-revival is in an even position##4
2. House:colonial == Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | tea | water |
| House     | colonial    | gothic-revival   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Birthday: june, january
Music-Genre: ambient, folk
1. Music-Genre:ambient is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:january is on the left of Birthday:june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Birthday   | january | june        |
| Music-Genre      | ambient  | folk |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
City: paris, boston
Sport: sailing, swimming
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. City:boston is on the left of City:paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | boston    | paris |
| Sport   | sailing | swimming |

