.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
Pet: fish, rat
Job: nurse, dressmaker
1. Pet:rat is on the right of Pet:fish##1
2. Job:dressmaker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | fish      | rat |
| Job       | nurse | dressmaker    |

